id: REQ-reasoning-logged
kind: requirement
name: Reasoning field logged on every VLM decision
status: draft
description: Every JSON command returned by the VLM shall include a non-empty `reasoning` field. The planner shall log this field verbatim to the decisions.jsonl audit trail on every planning cycle, along with the triggering event and the resulting command.
derives_from: NEED-explainable-decisions
verification_status: passing
satisfied_by: CMP-planner
verified_by: VER-reasoning-logged
